        ('R-FA8ESG', 9, 54, 3, 7, 'Разработка территориальных справочников', '<h2><h1>1) Umumiy talablar</h1></h2><h2><h2>1.1. Texnik stack</h2><ul><li>Backend: <strong>Laravel 11</strong></li><li>Ma’lumotlar bazasi: <strong>PostgreSQL 14+</strong></li><li>Admin UI: <strong>FilamentPHP v3</strong> (Resource, RelationManager, Filters, Tables, Forms)</li><li>PHP: 8.2+</li></ul></h2><h2><h2>1.2. Konvensiyalar</h2><ul><li>Har bir spravochnik uchun: id (bigIncrements), name (jsonb not null), code (string, unique, not null), status (boolean default true), order_index (int, nullable), created_at/updated_at, deleted_at (soft deletes).</li><li>name dagi kalitlar <strong>languages</strong> jadvalidagi tillarga mos. CRUD formda har bir aktiv til uchun alohida input ko‘rinadi.</li><li>code uchun <strong>unique</strong> indeks va <strong>case-insensitive</strong> unikalik (PostgreSQL citext yoki lower(code) ga unique index).</li><li>jsonb ustuni uchun GIN indeks (name bo‘yicha tez qidiruv uchun).</li><li>Barcha iyerarxik bog‘lanishlar <strong>foreign key</strong> bilan mustahkamlanadi (masalan, regions.country_id, cities.region_id, districts.city_id, mahallas.district_id) — bu hujjatdagi iyerarxiyaga mos ravishda&nbsp;<br><br>2d31e9e9-3317-4877-831d-a318913…&nbsp;<br><br>2d31e9e9-3317-4877-831d-a318913….</li><li>Har bir jadval uchun <strong>Migration</strong>, <strong>Eloquent Model</strong>, <strong>Seeder</strong>, <strong>Filament Resource</strong> talab qilinadi.</li></ul></h2><h2><h2>1.3. Translyatsiya (ko‘p tillilik)</h2><ul><li>languages jadvali: code (masalan: uz, ru, en, cy), name, status.</li><li>name (jsonb) qiymatlari: { "uz": "...", "ru": "...", "en": "..." } ko‘rinishida.</li><li>Validatsiya qoidasi: name JSON kalitlari languages.code (status=true) to‘plamidan tashqariga chiqmasin (form validatsiyasi + model rule).</li><li>Indeks: CREATE INDEX idx_tbl_name_gin ON table_name USING GIN (name jsonb_path_ops);</li></ul></h2><h2><h2>1.4. Filament talablar</h2><ul><li>Har bir spravochnik uchun: <strong>List, Create, Edit, View, Delete</strong> (soft delete bilan).</li><li>Jadvalda: code, status (badge/switch), name[default_locale] (masalan, name-&gt;&gt;''uz'' birlamchi ko‘rsatish), qidiruv, <strong>Filters</strong> (status, parent bo‘lsa — parent filter).</li><li>Forma: Repeater/KeyValue emas, balki <strong>dinamik ko‘rinish</strong>: aktiv tillar ro‘yxati bo‘yicha ko‘p inputlar (masalan, TextInput(''name.uz''), TextInput(''name.ru'')...).</li><li>Audit: created_by, updated_by (agar kerak bo‘lsa) — optional.</li></ul></h2><p><strong>Hududiy ma’lumotlar</strong> (Territorial)</p><p><strong>Iyerarxiya</strong>: Mamlakat → Viloyat(Oblast) → Shahar → Tuman → Mahalla (Mahalla qo‘mitasi)&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Jadvallar:</strong></p><ol><li>countries — (name jsonb, code, status)<ul><li>Maqsad: hujjatda <strong>Страна</strong> (grazhdanstvo/yo‘nalishlar)&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li>regions — (country_id fk, name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>Область (город)</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>cities — (region_id fk, name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>Город</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>districts — (city_id fk, name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>Район</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>mahalla — (district_id fk, name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>Махаллинский комитет</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>military_districts — (name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>Военный округ</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>udo — (name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>УДО</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>odo— (name jsonb, code, status) — <strong>ОДО</strong> (rayon darajasida)&nbsp;<br><br></li></ol><p><strong>Filament:</strong></p><ul><li>CountryResource → RelationManagers: Regions</li><li>RegionResource → Relation: Country, Cities</li><li>CityResource → Relation: Region, Districts</li><li>DistrictResource → Relation: City, Mahallas</li><li>MahallaResource</li><li>MilitaryDistrictResource, UdoResource, OdoResource</li></ul><p><br></p>', null, null, '2025-09-10 16:28:30', '2025-10-07 10:27:37', 3, null),
        ('R-WSXYC6', 9, 54, 3, 7, 'Разработка справочников по образованию', '<h2>Umumiy talablar (Qisqa)</h2><p><strong>Texnik stack:</strong></p><ul><li>Laravel 11, PHP 8.2+</li><li>PostgreSQL 14+</li><li>FilamentPHP v3 (Resource, RelationManager, Filters, Tables, Forms)</li></ul><p><strong>Konvensiyalar:</strong></p><ul><li>Har bir spravochnik jadvalda:<ul><li>id (bigIncrements), name (jsonb not null), code (string, unique, not null), status (boolean, default true), order_index (int, nullable), timestamps, softDeletes.</li></ul></li><li>name ustuni JSONB, tillar languages jadvalidagi aktiv kodlarga mos.</li><li>code case-insensitive unique (citext yoki lower(code) indeksi).</li><li>name ustuniga GIN indeks.</li><li>Iyerarxik bog‘lanishlar foreign key orqali (regions.country_id, cities.region_id, districts.city_id, mahallas.district_id).</li><li>Har bir jadval uchun: Migration, Model, Seeder, Filament Resource.</li></ul><p><strong>Ko‘p tillilik:</strong></p><ul><li>languages jadvali: code, name, status.</li><li>name qiymati: { "uz": "...", "ru": "...", "en": "..." }.</li><li>Validatsiya: faqat languages jadvalidagi aktiv tillarga mos kalitlar.</li></ul><p><strong>Filament talablar:</strong></p><ul><li>CRUD (List, Create, Edit, View, Delete, soft delete bilan).</li><li>Jadvalda: code, status (switch/badge), name (asosiy til), qidiruv va filtrlar.</li><li>Forma: aktiv tillar bo‘yicha alohida inputlar (name.uz, name.ru, name.en).</li><li>Audit maydonlari (created_by, updated_by) .<br><br><br></li></ul><h2>Ta’lim</h2><ul><li><strong>EducationalInstitution</strong></li><li><strong>InstitutionType</strong> (FK → EducationalInstitution)</li><li><strong>EducationSpecialty</strong> (FK → InstitutionType)</li><li><strong>EducationDegree</strong></li><li><strong>EducationType</strong></li><li><strong>EducationForm</strong></li><li><strong>Duration</strong></li><li><strong>DiplomaType</strong></li><li><strong>DiplomaStatus</strong> (FK → DiplomaType)</li><li><strong>TestingLanguage</strong></li><li><strong>TestingResults</strong> (FK → TestingLanguage)</li><li><strong>DirectionOfStudy</strong> (FK → EducationalInstitution, EducationSpecialty)</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', null, null, '2025-09-10 16:36:38', '2025-10-07 10:27:36', 3, null),
